        "setup": "Create a PagerDuty service with service type `Generic API` as described in the Events API v1 schema at [reference/events-v1/openapiv3.json](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PagerDuty/api-schema/main/reference/events-v1/openapiv3.json). The service detail page exposes the `service_key`, which you send in Events API v1 requests.",
        "acquisition": "manual"
